ppymyJq1SmI.title: Greece Island Market Spree!
ppymyJq1SmI.description:
Today, we're out in Greece as I take you to multiple cities and islands to adventure on and hustle for all the greatest gear! We start out in Athens then go to Crete Island, Mykonos, Syros and then end at Santorini! It's a proper adventure as we bargain for Yeezy, Air Jordan, Moncler, Fjallraven Kanken and much more! So grab some popcorn because we're just gonna go-go-go! Come along and enjoy the ride!

-Thanks to @Food X Bert  for coming along to these islands! 
 Go show him some love and subscribe to his channel!

00:00-26:49 Athens
26:50-41:44 Crete Island (Chania)
41:45-46:26 Crete Island (Heraklion)

T0TLOmG7XjQ.title: China's Epidemically Bad Translations
T0TLOmG7XjQ.description:
Living here for some time now, there has always been one thing that I just couldn't get over... The fact that these companies pay money to post their advertisements around the city, yet can't be bothered to get a correct translation. So I take you into ONE subway hall and show you how many translation errors I can spot within 30 feet of each other
